---
title: Carb Smart Bacon-Wrapped Asparagus with Salad and Avocado Dressing
description: Everything's better with bacon! Wrap tender spears of asparagus in strips of smoky bacon! They roast together to become charming bundles of fun!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/asperges-enroulees-de-bacon-b817b9bb.jpg
